OL,3,CDigital screening could replace
OL,4,Cbiopsies to diagnose bowel disease
OL,6,FResearchers have found a way to check
OL,7,Ffor the disease using digital
OL,8,Fscreenings
OL,10,FThe need for invasive biopsies when
OL,11,Fdiagnosing could become a thing of the
OL,12,Fpast as researchers have found a way
OL,13,Fto check for the disease using digital
OL,14,Fscreenings.
OL,16,FResearch was conducted by the Glasgow-
OL,17,Fbased scientists on behalf of , who
OL,18,Fsaid imaging technology can be used
OL,19,Finstead of biopsies when diagnosing
OL,20,Fthe disease.
