OL,3,CDigital screening could replace
OL,4,Cbiopsies to diagnose bowel disease
OL,6,FBiopsies require an invasive procedure
OL,7,Fwith a number of health risks, such as
OL,8,Finfection, and are limited in what
OL,9,Fthey can capture within a patient's
OL,10,Fbowel.
OL,12,FHowever, experts working with Cancer
OL,13,FResearch UK found that Positron
OL,14,FEmission Tomography (PET) imaging can
OL,15,Fallow the entire bowel to be examined
OL,16,Fand for tumours to be studied while
OL,17,Finside the body, as opposed to
OL,18,Fexamining the tumour tissue once it
OL,19,Fhas been removed.
