OL,6,FPET scans create a three-dimensional
OL,7,Fpicture of the inside of the body, and
OL,8,Fresearchers believe doing several
OL,9,Fscans during treatment could help
OL,10,Fmonitor the cancer more effectively.
OL,12,FThis approach of targeting treatment
OL,13,Fto a specific patient is known as
OL,14,Fprecision medicine, a growing area of
OL,15,Foncology.
