OL,6,FDr David Lewis, of the Cancer Research
OL,7,FUK Scotland Institute and the
OL,8,FUniversity of Glasgow, who led the
OL,9,Fresearch, said: "Precision medicine
OL,10,Fhas the potential to revolutionise
OL,11,Fcancer diagnosis and treatment.
OL,13,F"However, the development of accurate,
OL,14,Finformative and patient-friendly
OL,15,Fdiagnostic techniques is crucial for
OL,16,Fits success.
