OL,4,Cbiopsies to diagnose bowel disease
OL,6,F"PET imaging offers a promising
OL,7,Falternative, with the ability to
OL,8,Fsurvey the entire cancer landscape,
OL,9,Fallowing us to examine tumours in more
OL,10,Fdetail while they are still growing."
OL,12,FAccording to Cancer Research UK, about
OL,13,F4,000 people are diagnosed with bowel
OL,14,Fcancer in Scotland annually, and
OL,15,Faround 1,800 people diagnosed with the
OL,16,Fdisease die each year.
OL,18,FThe research team used existing
OL,19,Fgenetic data on bowel cancer to
OL,20,Fidentify different tumour
OL,21,Fcharacteristics using PET imaging.
