OL,6,FThey were also able to discover
OL,7,Fseveral different types of bowel
OL,8,Fcancer in mice based on their genes.
OL,10,FDr Catherine Elliott, director of
OL,11,Fresearch at Cancer Research UK, said:
OL,12,F"These findings by the team at the
OL,13,FCancer Research UK Scotland Institute
OL,14,Fand University of Glasgow offer an
OL,15,Fexciting opportunity to revolutionise
OL,16,Fthe way we diagnose and monitor bowel
OL,17,Fcancer without invasive surgery,
OL,18,Freducing the risk and improving
OL,19,Foutcomes for patients.
